# Components Architecture

## Layout Components
- **Layout**: [components/Layout.tsx](mdc:components/Layout.tsx) - Main page layout wrapper
- **Navbar**: [components/Navbar.tsx](mdc:components/Navbar.tsx) - Navigation bar component
- **Footer**: [components/Footer.tsx](mdc:components/Footer.tsx) - Site footer
- **Header**: [components/Header.tsx](mdc:components/Header.tsx) - Page header component

## UI Components
- **Section**: [components/Section.tsx](mdc:components/Section.tsx) - Content section wrapper
- **Heading**: [components/Heading.tsx](mdc:components/Heading.tsx) - Styled heading component
- **NavLink**: [components/NavLink.tsx](mdc:components/NavLink.tsx) - Navigation link component
- **Alerts**: [components/Alerts.tsx](mdc:components/Alerts.tsx) - Toast notifications

## Feature Components
- **Form Components**: [components/Form/](mdc:components/Form) - Form-related components
- **Menu Components**: [components/Menu/](mdc:components/Menu) - Menu display components
- **Map Components**: [components/Map/](mdc:components/Map) - Leaflet map components
- **Icons**: [components/Icons/](mdc:components/Icons) - Custom icon components
- **Masonry**: [components/Masonry/](mdc:components/Masonry) - Gallery layout components
- **Drag & Drop**: [components/DnD/](mdc:components/DnD) - Sortable components

## Admin Components
- **Admin HOC**: [lib/withAdminNav.tsx](mdc:lib/withAdminNav.tsx) - Higher-order component for admin navigation

## Component Guidelines
- Uses React Bootstrap for consistent styling
- TypeScript for type safety
- Responsive design with Bootstrap classes
- Reusable components follow single responsibility principle
- Test files located in `components/__tests__/` directories
